    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >由东映动画与独立开发者Nestopi共同开发的《Re:VER PROJECT TOKYO》是一款以像素画表现的现代东京为背景的生存悬疑冒险游戏。被诬陷为“无罪之罪”的主人公弥音雪乃一边逃避警察，一边利用其生存技能努力活下来，寻找真正的罪犯。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >作为一个被广泛认知的通缉犯，主人公无法通过“购物”来填饱肚子。有时得靠路边捡到的橡果，有时则要从垃圾箱中找到汉堡包来生存。当健康有了足够的保障后，再开始活动来“证明清白”。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3097730/extras/254001b3f00c7f9a00a8b97ec2d98fe6.poster.avif?t=1764560158\" width=640 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3097730/extras/254001b3f00c7f9a00a8b97ec2d98fe6.webm?t=1764560158\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3097730/extras/254001b3f00c7f9a00a8b97ec2d98fe6.mp4?t=1764560158\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >同伴“六实雏树”</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >主人公将与同样被诬陷的偶像六实雏树一起在东京都内辗转多个“藏身处”过着逃亡生活。由于偶像是名人，不能轻易外出。同伴能否生存全靠玩家的物资收集能力。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3097730/extras/c62c66ebf2f8ba66effa7127e9ce50f3.poster.avif?t=1764560158\" width=640 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3097730/extras/c62c66ebf2f8ba66effa7127e9ce50f3.webm?t=1764560158\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3097730/extras/c62c66ebf2f8ba66effa7127e9ce50f3.mp4?t=1764560158\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >市民传感系统</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在这个相互监视的社会里，东京市民（NPC）对奇怪行为非常敏感。玩家必须在不引起市民注意的情况下搜寻垃圾箱，否则会引起市民的不适，这将有助于警方的调查。<br> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3097730/extras/d9fa24e8296cb2e000334de35c608556.poster.avif?t=1764560158\" width=640 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3097730/extras/d9fa24e8296cb2e000334de35c608556.webm?t=1764560158\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3097730/extras/d9fa24e8296cb2e000334de35c608556.mp4?t=1764560158\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >重生的故事</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在这个东京，被认为“堕落的人再也无法浮现”。无论是真罪还是冤罪。一旦被贴上异端者的标签并被社会排斥，人生就结束了。即便在这样严酷的大都会东京，二人仍然站起来，努力克服困难。他们最终会到达天堂还是地狱，只有玩家能见证他们的命运。 </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >细致描绘真实东京的像素艺术</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >本作特意去除了赛博朋克元素，旨在通过像素表现“真实的东京”。不仅是新宿或涩谷，还呈现了只有日本人才能描绘的真正的东京。 </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >老牌动画制作公司与独立开发者的融合</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >本作由拥有70年历史的动画制作公司东映动画和日本独立开发者Nestopi合作。Nestopi以少人数团队持续挑战开发创新系统游戏，而东映动画则凭借多年积累的专业知识擅长制作故事和艺术。两者的结合为独立游戏带来了新的风潮。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >操作手册</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3097730/extras/85ae1529fd6f85e8b6fff88aff05b7c7.avif?t=1764560158\" width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3097730/extras/6736bbf545d51a3c126824df68021b22.avif?t=1764560158\" width=800 height=450 /></span></p>",
